title: Killers Amongst Us: Real Life "Hell's Kitchen," Gorgeous Restauranteur Disappears. What happened to Dawn? (part 4)
itunes:title: Killers Amongst Us: Real Life "Hell's Kitchen," Gorgeous Restauranteur Disappears. What happened to Dawn? (part 4)
description:
The pieces of the puzzle are beginning to fall into place for detectives, and a new person of interest comes to light. Cops learn hard on good old-fashion street work to figure out what happened to Dawn Viens. The answer may have been right in front of them the whole time.
